{"tid":2325901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《蘋果》一定撐落去 關關難過關關過","createTime":"2020-12-15T02:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T02:35:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"02461db1ef8923ad029a43624b6e2d17f90d4cc7","tid":2325901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T02:35:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/7W2ZQDSUS5E4TG5TKXDPMKLOJY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2F7W2ZQDSUS5E4TG5TKXDPMKLOJY%2F&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7n5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=93116943\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2F7W2ZQDSUS5E4TG5TKXDPMKLOJY%2F&h=a5ff6393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/7W2ZQDSUS5E4TG5TKXDPMKLOJY/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》一定撐落去 關關難過關關過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j_VXGAZ7vVsJj6DFfRKRGghTmF0=/988x740/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WRWXPNOSHJCHXKV2RDTL5FS5HE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj_VXGAZ7vVsJj6DFfRKRGghTmF0%3D%2F988x740%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWRWXPNOSHJCHXKV2RDTL5FS5HE.gif&h=8262576e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有讀者提前送來聖誕卡，希望黎智英早日獲批保釋。<br />\n<br />\n極權用盡辦法掩藏和打壓真相，卻無減真相價值半分。多位讀者來函支持壹傳媒創辦人黎智英，更有人提前送來聖誕賀卡，希望他早日獲准保釋。一名「見閻王前一秒也要看蘋果日報」的讀者親筆來信，寫滿四頁紙。他讚揚黎智英不舔共，選擇為快要沉淪的香港大聲呼疾，辦報堅守言論陣地，抗擊黨報顛倒是非，即使面對中共以「拉人封報」攻勢封殺，黎亦未有懼色。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：下周三申保釋 國安官負責<br />\n<br />\n有小讀者來函憶起8.11「蘋果圍戰」，想起黎生「《蘋果》一定撐落去！」的豪言。有讀者形容2020年香港動盪不安，眼見黎智英被捕，日後可能波及更多記者，「我們只可眼白白地見證着，不知又有多少手足面臨鐵柵之苦，不知極權何時完結，不知香港重現光明的時候」。但她鼓勵同路人，就算要頭破血流，都要拚命做下去，「難以在香港撼動極權政府，便跳出香港，讓全世界知道，永留青史。就算危機四伏，關關難過關關過，在自己份內盡力而為，對嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bt7DICLrgAI6fEagHjkLqnhyclk=/1481x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JZKJDBSYT5HPVOFEY2YE24IKH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fbt7DICLrgAI6fEagHjkLqnhyclk%3D%2F1481x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJZKJDBSYT5HPVOFEY2YE24IKH4.jpg&h=629ee8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你不會孤軍作戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/grlAugFIDnNBKz8ltI86oTCb4-g=/1275x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MHHRPISNUNEJPNSYYUTXEUGZK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgrlAugFIDnNBKz8ltI86oTCb4-g%3D%2F1275x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMHHRPISNUNEJPNSYYUTXEUGZK4.jpg&h=7da64d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面對極權 毫不畏懼"}]}